Title: No Time Like The Present
Description:
Emberthal arrived while you were in the field. She and her allies are surveying the area from the cliffs above. 

It would be wise to check in with her, I think. We would not want her to attempt taking the Reach alone.
ObjectivesText: Meet with Emberthal above the cliffs of Morqut Village.

Objectives.Text: Meet with Scalecommander Emberthal above Morqut Village
